    "facility": "GKN Aerospace, Garden Grove, CA",
    "started_iso": "2026-05-21T22:40:00Z",
    "status_headline": "Incident resolved, Day 9 recovery. All evacuations lifted May 27 at 7:30 PM PDT. GKN tank stable; 300-ft exclusion zone remains on Western Ave. OC Board Chair Chaffee calls on GKN to open compensation claims process for ~50,000 displaced residents. Mass tort exceeds 100 plaintiffs; DA criminal investigation ongoing. Community impact survey at ggcity.org/hazmat-incident/survey.",
